packaging for the following platforms:

redhat          - Redhat, Centos, OpenSUSE/SLES
debian          - Debian, Ubuntu
archlinux       - ArchLinux
slackware       - Slackware packaging
freebsd         - FreeBSD standalone package (not ports, pkg for 8,9 and pkgng for 10)
netbsd          - NetBSD standalon package (not ports, not pkgsrc)
solaris         - packaging for Solaris
windows         - WIX MSI installer setup creation
obs             - OpenSUSE build service (build.opensuse.org)
patches         - patches for all kind of software and systems,
                  needed when building Wolframe
tools           - various tools to build a release and to to build packages
